{"tid":558531,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（多圖）東京熱門景點＋圍住富士山自駕溫泉動物十天","createTime":"2018-02-12T10:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T15:53:01.000Z","uid":147233,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"454c93168e7e6d3116321d08412310366ae6304e","tid":558531,"uid":147233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:55:34.000Z","msg":"Day 1<br />\n對上一次去日本已經係兩年前大阪 今次東京都內會玩六日 中間四日圍住個富士山自駕 我吹屎眼同我女友patpat小姐都係第一次去東京同自駕遊 開始啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/185041_20753378a4b88ac49bf912d9727d813d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F185041_20753378a4b88ac49bf912d9727d813d.png&h=3dc03846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/185043_ef357f7f18b5420e6b0177522cc5c3ba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F185043_ef357f7f18b5420e6b0177522cc5c3ba.png&h=8728fac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n快運中午一點機 好彩無delay 不過下次去可能會搵下其他 行李簡位加埋都唔平 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/185137_660e41e8c177f27afc6165befbe76b64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F185137_660e41e8c177f27afc6165befbe76b64.png&h=a636d952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/185139_ac37c923bd80f6f5bcf83bcb5cd79da3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F185139_ac37c923bd80f6f5bcf83bcb5cd79da3.png&h=894379a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到成田已經天黑 當日有d雨 零下五度 落機一刻已經打哂牙教<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/185233_d6a3017a4a6d4b7f6cb57ac9fac15490.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F185233_d6a3017a4a6d4b7f6cb57ac9fac15490.png&h=ee8a2a55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/185238_e9e654cf49f0b28ceb56ef72bbdb6fc9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F185238_e9e654cf49f0b28ceb56ef72bbdb6fc9.png&h=ca97755e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSkyliner 開餐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頭2day住上野 搭skyliner好適合 佢好似係新幹線以外最快既列車 加來回同地鐵pass買低好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/185324_2275910ef21b1fb24b7b9bc71232ce8d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F185324_2275910ef21b1fb24b7b9bc71232ce8d.png&h=8250948c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80fe02b3d8bba9cf1fa98ae6a4ec5b8cf23f7a0c","tid":558531,"uid":147233,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:06:04.000Z","msg":"Day 1<br />\n<br />\n去到京成上野站 行去我地今日既酒店 上野東金屋 離上野站同阿美橫丁好近 價格又平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/185653_a847f2a245663a38d84f23207a04b522.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F185653_a847f2a245663a38d84f23207a04b522.png&h=c7892550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/185656_c39fb30f84064e71019748410e1508cc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F185656_c39fb30f84064e71019748410e1508cc.png&h=27014010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大就一定唔大 但又唔算細<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n休息陣要出去食晚飯 已經8點 patpat小姐自上次大阪食完饑丸水產念念不忘 第一餐就食返佢招牌既蟹蓋 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/185752_96a1dbbb7fa4561f0656fc3b9feb6876.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F185752_96a1dbbb7fa4561f0656fc3b9feb6876.png&h=3f87ad37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/185757_b22af022f37a7a65bbf7cae0ae73b17e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F185757_b22af022f37a7a65bbf7cae0ae73b17e.png&h=c6065b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加埋杯有酒精既果汁酒 好撚正<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/185910_9832afcf0c29cdd9cc01d1c0f52cb000.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F185910_9832afcf0c29cdd9cc01d1c0f52cb000.png&h=b7896c83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/185934_ee10c8ab13ed9d39180a93fb2842da0a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F185934_ee10c8ab13ed9d39180a93fb2842da0a.png&h=fbe12741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有屎眼仔最愛既茶漬飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完一出黎由落雨變左落雪 嘩 我第一次見雪 仲要喺東京見 真係好難得 出發前一星期就係東京大雪 今次相對較微<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/190049_fb50d9a4315475ab5b340abec9e7e9ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F190049_fb50d9a4315475ab5b340abec9e7e9ae.png&h=0f5cd3ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/190055_b2db8a2e37dfe3edfbd85c2459793718.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F190055_b2db8a2e37dfe3edfbd85c2459793718.png&h=c3008078&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/190057_a1fccdb6e8329af7040a57361d306391.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F190057_a1fccdb6e8329af7040a57361d306391.png&h=b8fff78b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地又影又玩雪 日本人就好似好討厭落雨 由我地自high 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/190202_febb9fcfa1fc0ce0ad267e1625f11af6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F190202_febb9fcfa1fc0ce0ad267e1625f11af6.png&h=15a60d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/190204_01dbe9b983d14194f3f2cdae9b0b1a82.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F190204_01dbe9b983d14194f3f2cdae9b0b1a82.png&h=03e93e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/190213_9cdd6c48f053b7b1777b1d80efeac2cc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F190213_9cdd6c48f053b7b1777b1d80efeac2cc.png&h=4b32c2c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夜晚開既舖頭都冇咩 去左阿美橫丁夾下公仔 再食埋宵夜 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/190307_362838f6465528fb517b7963b06b0a80.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F190307_362838f6465528fb517b7963b06b0a80.png&h=b8c80066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/190311_ee29c468ac2084ba73ca678aa203b754.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F190311_ee29c468ac2084ba73ca678aa203b754.png&h=6738ef21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/190313_e290ded67b92f3e97cf76dc9ced78344.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F190313_e290ded67b92f3e97cf76dc9ced78344.png&h=811dc231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n博多風龍 以為好普通 原來都幾多日本人食 湯底好似一蘭 甚至好食過 仲可以加麵免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返酒店明天繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一吹寫遊記 多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2d8a6f606083788a81b616b87b8ff2f6663b67","tid":558531,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:10:04.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76523e07ad7dfcbf7ea26592d83a3ce136f8ebf9","tid":558531,"uid":34047,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"睇到 東京熱 先入黎"},{"pid":"028d02fdebd653af2faacc79120b6f2aaddb46ad","tid":558531,"uid":147233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"Day 2<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/191413_835ac8fc6154fa0bc183e8c3e34fb893.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F191413_835ac8fc6154fa0bc183e8c3e34fb893.png&h=01f8df2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/191418_8c8df843a492639543cf7dc362b09ffd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F191418_8c8df843a492639543cf7dc362b09ffd.png&h=1d759b75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日繼續落雪 不過只係維持到12點中午 對於我地係好事 因為太凍 拎遮又煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/191332_f3eb636add9132b2da48b810071dab06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F191332_f3eb636add9132b2da48b810071dab06.png&h=74041c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一站築地 今年十月搬 所以係第一次/最尾一次去 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/191526_84568325053e442570733af67db926e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F191526_84568325053e442570733af67db926e0.png&h=58ead39a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/191536_57af3d79dc02a71ce1226b41fa8ccb63.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F191536_57af3d79dc02a71ce1226b41fa8ccb63.png&h=f762c896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地冇咁神心去排壽司大 只係喺場外d小店食小食<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/191638_dfa8c6b54cd2263c2c034edddc5472c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F191638_dfa8c6b54cd2263c2c034edddc5472c7.png&h=557211d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/191642_31fc16f70379bfa171e6eb82e71cb8c2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F191642_31fc16f70379bfa171e6eb82e71cb8c2.png&h=59c5358e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/191648_a413f0306489a19434c52c08738839f6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F191648_a413f0306489a19434c52c08738839f6.png&h=4b229049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玉子燒好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/191755_187f277542bc7b9be729d5bab0bd63ba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F191755_187f277542bc7b9be729d5bab0bd63ba.png&h=3c5823a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/191802_a05cda17006006f94ee035f0fb7ddfb0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F191802_a05cda17006006f94ee035f0fb7ddfb0.png&h=f13253c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n燒海鮮貴呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/191853_551320b5c4a3276c78b7e8b29858b9a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F191853_551320b5c4a3276c78b7e8b29858b9a1.png&h=bc8c8552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/191856_625dd2acbb63937ea58e9786b55bdb01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F191856_625dd2acbb63937ea58e9786b55bdb01.png&h=f3e9d52e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/191902_f2507c092959450e701bd71043f6a536.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F191902_f2507c092959450e701bd71043f6a536.png&h=c1dc0135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 一邊落雪一邊食嘢一邊影相一邊膽遮<br />\n狠狽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/191944_593e97f53d060ff87e68ed38288528de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F191944_593e97f53d060ff87e68ed38288528de.png&h=64d7c4d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完早餐 一餐好貴既早餐 好彩只係黎一次 <br />\n<br />\n行路去銀座.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95ed3ac7f068932ce8fc80a702bb07275a44289","tid":558531,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:27:52.000Z","msg":"非常寫實而且有參考價值<br />\n留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a98e2e09ad7cd6eed1151b739c5f5a02fe1fdc","tid":558531,"uid":147233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b95ed3ac7f068932ce8fc80a702bb07275a44289","tid":558531,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:27:52.000Z","msg":"非常寫實